KeysToEntries.1_11_1-01: Got a tail coming up fast…
KeysToEntries.1_11_1-04:
Doesn’t look that fast…
might as well have some fun…
KeysToEntries.1_11_1-05: …Heh, I thought we were keeping a low profile?
KeysToEntries.1_11_1-06: Once in a while… why not?
KeysToEntries.1_11_1-07:
Drifting’s as easy as breakfast…
it’s my specialty.
KeysToEntries.1_11_1-10:
Stop it! Keisuke of Project D
wouldn’t say that!
KeysToEntries.1_11_1-12:
Alright then… here comes
Keisuke’s technique…!
KeysToEntries.1_11_1-18:
With due respect… Fujiwara here…
my game is flawless control.
KeysToEntries.1_11_1-19:
An inside pass on me…
that’s not a thing‼
KeysToEntries.1_11_2-1:
You’re the type to face
Purple Shadow next, right?
KeysToEntries.1_11_2-2: Honestly, those guys are no joke.
KeysToEntries.1_11_2-3: Even Fujiwara and Keisuke only barely won…
KeysToEntries.1_11_2-4:
Old friends’ privilege…
I’ll brief you on the course.
KeysToEntries.1_11_2-5:
This course has lots of
long, sweeping corners.
KeysToEntries.1_11_2-6: Blind exits mean no letup… hard to send it.
KeysToEntries.1_11_2-7: (…All borrowed from Fujiwara and Keisuke, though.)
KeysToEntries.1_11_2-8: Yo, hold up! I’m helping here!
KeysToEntries.1_11_3-1:
Rule is… whoever wins 
takes on the mountain god.
KeysToEntries.1_11_3-5:
As a warm-up,
there’s no better battle than this…!
KeysToEntries.1_11_3-9:
…Heh, Daiki gets passed
this easily, huh…
KeysToEntries.1_11_3-14: Now I just hold the lead and win!
KeysToEntries.1_11_3-15:
Purple Shadow and Todo School
have been rivals for years…
KeysToEntries.1_11_3-16: Whoever you are, I’m not giving this up…!
KeysToEntries.1_11_3-17: How do you stay on throttle there…!?
KeysToEntries.1_11_3-18: How much stronger can you get, you bastard!!
KeysToEntries.1_11_4-1: I’ll give you my full effort.
KeysToEntries.1_11_4-4: No wonder Ryosuke vouches for you.
KeysToEntries.1_11_4-7: There’s still excess in your inputs.
KeysToEntries.1_11_4-9:
Don’t be disappointed…
it’s not that you’re bad.
KeysToEntries.1_11_4-10: There’s no doubt you have outstanding talent…
KeysToEntries.1_11_4-11: If you can turn this experience into fuel to grow, that’s good…
KeysToEntries.1_11_4-12: Now then… I’ll run away… no need to save tires…
KeysToEntries.1_11_4-13:
I’ll burn the remaining grip and
disappear from your sight‼
KeysToEntries.1_11_4-16:
How… you shouldn’t have
enough tire left for this…
KeysToEntries.1_11_5-2: I don’t spend time reading folks.
KeysToEntries.1_11_5-3: All gas from the start… quick finish‼
KeysToEntries.1_11_5-6:
Opening the gap‼
Foot down, mouth on‼
KeysToEntries.1_11_5-10: Good… I see why Jo gets hyped‼
KeysToEntries.1_11_5-16:
…Don’t downplay
how I mesh with this R34‼
KeysToEntries.1_11_5-20:
Heh… impressive…‼
Had me stunned for a sec…!
KeysToEntries.1_11_5-22:
We’re past reason here…
no one gets to judge…‼
KeysToEntries.1_11_5-24: Damn it… half a tire’s width understeer, huh⁉
